    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer

    public class PeaShooterPlant
extends OffensivePlant
    This class contains the data for making a standard peashooter class. HP can is controlled by MAX_HP. Attack speed is dictated by OffensivePlant.DEFAULT_SHOOT_TRIGGER.
